Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,35,,-= 小红帽 =-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满月了  今晚锁好门窗\N{\fs45}Full moon. Lock up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人带走猪  总比带走你好点\N{\fs45}Better the wolf takes the pig than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们住在黑暗森林的边缘\N{\fs45}We lived on the edge of a dark forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的村子鲜有人知\N{\fs45}Few knew our village by names
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不少人听说过这里骇人听闻的事件\N{\fs45}but many had heard of the terrible things that happened there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈总对我说\N{\fs45}My mother always told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别和陌生人说话\N{\fs45}"Don't talk to strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打完水马上回家\N{\fs45}Go get water and come straight home."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着做个听话的乖乖女\N{\fs45}I tried to be a good girI and do what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我试过了\N{\fs45}Believe me, I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs45}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带刀了吗\N{\fs45}Do you have the knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带了\N{\fs45}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  雪白的毛\N{\fs45}Look, snow white fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以给你做双猎靴\N{\fs45}I'll make you a pair of hunting boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手啊  彼得\N{\fs45}Do it, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你动手\N{\fs45}You do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你来动手\N{\fs45}No, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,35,,十年后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收工吧\N{\fs45}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道好女孩不该猎杀兔子\N{\fs45}I know good girls aren't supposed to hunt rabbits
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或独自走入树林\N{\fs45}or go into the woods alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但打小起\N{\fs45}But since we were kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总有办法让我违反规则\N{\fs45}he always had a way of making me wanna break the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得  先吃饭再砍  树跑不了\N{\fs45}Peter! Trees'll still be there after we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我\N{\fs45}Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿什么来换\N{\fs45}What will you give me for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没告诉你吗\N{\fs45}They didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我什么\N{\fs45}Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们决定把你嫁给亨利·拉扎\N{\fs45}They've arranged for you to marry Henry Lazar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈终于如愿了\N{\fs45}Well, my mother finally got what she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到金钱\N{\fs45}Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利也如愿以偿了  得到了你\N{\fs45}Henry gets what he's always wanted. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们怎么办\N{\fs45}So, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想嫁给他吗\N{\fs45}Do you want to marry him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我不想\N{\fs45}You know I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证明\N{\fs45}Prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么证明\N{\fs45}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起私奔\N{\fs45}Run away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去哪里\N{\fs45}Where would we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪里都行\N{\fs45}Anywhere you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游弋于大海\N{\fs45}The ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混迹于都市\N{\fs45}The city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐居于群山\N{\fs45}The mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕吗\N{\fs45}You afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不怕   -不怕吗\N{\fs45}- No. - Oh, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs45}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得离开家\N{\fs45}You'd leave your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的家人\N{\fs45}Your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的全部生活\N{\fs45}Your whole life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能和你在一起  我愿意做任何事\N{\fs45}I would do anything to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说\N{\fs45}I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美得你\N{\fs45}Oh, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心动不如马上行动\N{\fs45}Let's do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他们发现\N{\fs45}We have half a day's ride
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经跑出半天的路程了\N{\fs45}before anyone knows we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会追上你\N{\fs45}I'll race you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人来了\N{\fs45}The wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里  这边\N{\fs45}This way! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它又杀人了\N{\fs45}It killed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我们遵守约定  献祭过了啊\N{\fs45}But we've kept the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狼人违背了约定\N{\fs45}Well, the wolf has broken it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被杀的是谁\N{\fs45}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fs45}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你姐姐\N{\fs45}It's your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  爸爸\N{\fs45}Mother, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西\N{\fs45}Lucie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西\N{\fs45}Lucie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  克劳德\N{\fs45}Thank you, Claude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉扎夫人  请进\N{\fs45}Madame Lazar, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏塞特\N{\fs45}Suzette.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节哀顺变\N{\fs45}I'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs45}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来拿吧\N{\fs45}Let me take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  亨利\N{\fs45}Hello, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们好\N{\fs45}Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西是个好姑娘\N{\fs45}Lucie was a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在是你的未婚夫了\N{\fs45}He's your fiance now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他过来致哀\N{\fs45}He's come to offer his condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一点不了解他\N{\fs45}But I barely know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得去了解他\N{\fs45}You'll get to know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在下去吧  求你了\N{\fs45}Now go down there. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞泽尔\N{\fs45}Cesaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们去酒馆吧\N{\fs45}Come with us to the tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让女士们用她们自己的方式悼念\N{\fs45}Let the women grieve in their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我也要去\N{\fs45}I-- I-- I want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去\N{\fs45}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嫁给你父亲的时候  并不爱他\N{\fs45}I didn't love your father when we were first married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的我深爱着另一个男人\N{\fs45}I was in love with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我慢慢爱上了他\N{\fs45}But I came to love your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有了两个漂亮的女儿\N{\fs45}And he gave me two beautiful daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的祷告也管用吧\N{\fs45}We should count our blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  神父\N{\fs45}Come on, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人已经将近二十年没杀人了\N{\fs45}It's been almost 20 years since the wolf has taken a human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十年了\N{\fs45}Twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为每个满月\N{\fs45}That's because we sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们献上了最好的牲畜\N{\fs45}our best livestock every full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直信守约定\N{\fs45}We kept our end of the bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们要杀了它\N{\fs45}So now we kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs45}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们杀了这畜生\N{\fs45}Let's kill that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs45}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请来了所罗门神父\N{\fs45}I've summoned Father Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父\N{\fs45}Father Solomon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在全国各地\N{\fs45}He has destroyed werewolves and witches
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了不少狼人和巫女\N{\fs45}in cities throughout the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会帮我们干掉这野兽\N{\fs45}He will rid us of this beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs45}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会因为我们复仇心切而为所欲为\N{\fs45}He'll rob us of our vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奇怪她怎么会在月圆之夜出门呢\N{\fs45}I wonder why she was outside on a wolf night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是偷溜出去和男孩子约会吧\N{\fs45}Maybe she snuck out to meet a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西绝不会满脑子想男人\N{\fs45}My Lucie never even thought about boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定迷上了我的孙子\N{\fs45}She was certainly taken with my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她老是像只小狗一样缠着他\N{\fs45}She used to come by and follow him about like a puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出事那晚  她发现\N{\fs45}She found out that night that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利和她妹妹订婚了\N{\fs45}Henry was engaged to her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定悲痛欲绝\N{\fs45}She must have been heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她宁愿死  也不愿忍受没有他的日子\N{\fs45}Maybe she chose to die rather than live without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太浪漫了\N{\fs45}How romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯\N{\fs45}Prudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱说\N{\fs45}It's unspeakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她从没告诉过我\N{\fs45}She never even told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想多了  亲爱的\N{\fs45}Don't worry, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利的视线从没离开过你\N{\fs45}Henry always had his eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是最漂亮的\N{\fs45}You're the pretty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来致哀的\N{\fs45}I'm paying my respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你来干嘛\N{\fs45}I know exactly why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经失去一个女儿\N{\fs45}I've already lost one daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽是我的所有\N{\fs45}Valerie's all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么也给不了她\N{\fs45}You have nothing to offer her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有工作  和你丈夫一样\N{\fs45}I have a trade. The same one as your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道樵夫能挣多少钱\N{\fs45}I know what a woodcutter earns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利是她幸福生活的唯一希望\N{\fs45}Henry's her only hope for a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你爱她...\N{\fs45}If you love her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就该放手\N{\fs45}you'll let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在通往格瑞摩尔山的小路上\N{\fs45}We've all seen the bones
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都见过散落的骸骨\N{\fs45}on the trail to Mount Grimmoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人的老巢就在那里\N{\fs45}That's where the wolf makes its lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道狼人的弱点\N{\fs45}We know the weaknesses of the werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它白天不能出没\N{\fs45}It can't come out in daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不能踏上圣地\N{\fs45}It can't step onto holy ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还怕银器\N{\fs45}And there's silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银器可以杀死它\N{\fs45}That'll kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银器\N{\fs45}Silver!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许奥古斯特神父是对的\N{\fs45}Maybe Father Auguste is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们该等等\N{\fs45}Maybe we should wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懦夫\N{\fs45}Coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许  我的孩子\N{\fs45}Maybe, my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该鼓起勇气\N{\fs45}you should find your courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都想去猎狼吗\N{\fs45}You want to hunt the wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就去抓它\N{\fs45}Let's hunt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了它\N{\fs45}Let's kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了这野兽\N{\fs45}Let's kill the beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了它\N{\fs45}Let's kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了\N{\fs45}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  伙计们\N{\fs45}Come on, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起去猎狼\N{\fs45}Are you with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs45}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fs45}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了姐姐  不能再失去你\N{\fs45}I lost my sister. I can't lose you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能再这样了\N{\fs45}We can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得听他们的  你得嫁给亨利\N{\fs45}You have to go through with it. You have to marry Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道我想要的不是亨利\N{\fs45}But you know I don't want Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想那些有的没的了\N{\fs45}Don't make this something it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾有过欢乐  仅此而已\N{\fs45}Look, we had our fun. That's all it ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的不是真的\N{\fs45}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了东西给你\N{\fs45}I made something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想在婚礼上给你  但...\N{\fs45}I was gonna wait until our wedding, but, uh....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是以防万一\N{\fs45}Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会快乐起来的\N{\fs45}You will be happy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fs45}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  亨利\N{\fs45}Come on, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该等等\N{\fs45}We should wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该等等所罗门神父\N{\fs45}We should wait for Father Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs45}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明天就到了\N{\fs45}He'll be here tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会杀了狼人\N{\fs45}We're gonna kill the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会结果它的\N{\fs45}We can take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人齐了吗  还有人去吗\N{\fs45}That's it? Nobody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发\N{\fs45}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家找你妈妈去\N{\fs45}Go home to your mama's, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德里安  谢谢你为露西出头\N{\fs45}Adrian. Thank you for standing up for Lucie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很不容易\N{\fs45}That was no small thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就快成一家人了  换你也会这样做\N{\fs45}We'll be family soon. You'd have done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应我  千万要小心\N{\fs45}Promise me you'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs45}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人不要我  我全是骨头\N{\fs45}The wolf doesn't want me. I'm all gristle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是认真的  儿子\N{\fs45}I mean it, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会小心的  妈妈\N{\fs45}I promise, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶\N{\fs45}Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  亲爱的\N{\fs45}Darling. Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs45}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心\N{\fs45}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还有很多事没告诉我\N{\fs45}There are so many things she didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是她妹妹  应该无话不谈\N{\fs45}And I'm her sister. I should've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是她的选择\N{\fs45}That was her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都有秘密\N{\fs45}We all have secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得我奶奶以前常说\N{\fs45}Remember what my grandma used to say:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-面包可以缓解忧伤  -缓解忧伤\N{\fs45}- "All sorrows are less with bread."  - "Less with bread".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  试一试\N{\fs45}Here. Try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮\N{\fs45}How beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我为了你的婚礼做的\N{\fs45}I was making it for your wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得这是我的婚礼\N{\fs45}I don't feel like it's my wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得就像...\N{\fs45}I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是被卖了\N{\fs45}I'm being sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那里\N{\fs45}Right up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好小心点\N{\fs45}You better watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有岔口了\N{\fs45}There's a fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分头行动\N{\fs45}Let's split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一个岔口\N{\fs45}Another fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进陡峭的那个\N{\fs45}We'll take the steep one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我们该一起行动\N{\fs45}No. We should stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  亲爱的\N{\fs45}Good morning, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  奶奶\N{\fs45}Morning, Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶告诉过我们\N{\fs45}Grandmother told us that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人常常会灭了一家门\N{\fs45}the wolf used to kill entire families...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从床上掳走孩子们\N{\fs45}snatching children from their beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来不相信这些故事  直到现在\N{\fs45}Those stories never seemed real to me. Until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕碎这畜生\N{\fs45}Ripped the thing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德\N{\fs45}Claude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬艾德里安\N{\fs45}To Adrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了他的献身\N{\fs45}For his sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬艾德里安\N{\fs45}To Adrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的亨利\N{\fs45}Poor Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利\N{\fs45}Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲是位勇士\N{\fs45}Your father was a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  我离得很近  甚至能闻到它\N{\fs45}You know, I was close enough to smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我害怕了  躲了起来\N{\fs45}And I was afraid. And I hid from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做\N{\fs45}I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:23:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该去救他\N{\fs45}I should've saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亨利  -你走吧\N{\fs45}- Henry... - Just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让你看到我这样\N{\fs45}I don't want you to see me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.34,0:24:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亨利的父亲  对吗  你爱的人\N{\fs45}It was Henry's father, wasn't it? The man you loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西爱上了他\N{\fs45}Lucie was in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.52,0:24:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她比我大一岁  她应该可以嫁给他的\N{\fs45}She was a year older than me. She could've married him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.62,0:24:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非要我嫁呢\N{\fs45}Why did you insist it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.12,0:25:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你知道答案\N{\fs45}I think you know the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.86,0:25:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你亲口说出来\N{\fs45}I want you to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.00,0:25:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西是亨利的同父异母的妹妹\N{\fs45}Lucie was Henry's half-sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.73,0:25:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德里安是她的父亲\N{\fs45}Adrian was her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.27,0:25:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸知道吗\N{\fs45}Does papa know about Lucie?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.28,0:25:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道  你得保证严守这个秘密\N{\fs45}No. And you have to promise me that you'll never tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.15,0:25:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父\N{\fs45}Father Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.82,0:25:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\fs45}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.29,0:26:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德\N{\fs45}Claude.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.11,0:26:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下驾到\N{\fs45}Presenting His Eminence....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.05,0:26:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父\N{\fs45}Father Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.06,0:26:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs45}Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.49,0:26:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭\N{\fs45}Oh, please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.33,0:26:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看  看到这些孩子了吗\N{\fs45}You see? You see all these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.67,0:26:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们多么害怕啊\N{\fs45}You see how scared they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.17,0:26:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里有一只大恶狼  得有人杀了它\N{\fs45}There's a big, bad wolf. Someone has to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.14,0:27:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那只杀了我们妈妈的野兽吗\N{\fs45}Is that the beast that killed our mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.44,0:27:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能\N{\fs45}It may very well be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.18,0:27:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  我随后就到\N{\fs45}Go on. I'll join you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.55,0:27:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs45}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.18,0:27:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs45}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.67,0:27:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分荣幸  阁下\N{\fs45}This is indeed an honor, Your Eminence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.41,0:27:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  你正好赶上了我们的狂欢\N{\fs45}Welcome. You've arrived just in time for our festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.05,0:27:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所见  狼人已经搞定了\N{\fs45}As you can see, the werewolf has been dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是狼人\N{\fs45}That is not a werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.70,0:27:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧\N{\fs45}No disrespect...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.13,0:27:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们整整两代人深受这畜生所害\N{\fs45}but we have been living with this beast for two generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.10,0:28:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们当然知道对付的是什么\N{\fs45}We know what we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.84,0:28:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧\N{\fs45}Well, no disrespect...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.27,0:28:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你们完全不知道要对付的是什么\N{\fs45}but you have no idea what you are dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.91,0:28:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾像你一样\N{\fs45}I was like you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.35,0:28:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子名叫佩内洛普\N{\fs45}My wife's name was Penelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.59,0:28:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她给我生了两个漂亮的女儿\N{\fs45}She gave me two beautiful daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.72,0:28:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一家本来十分幸福\N{\fs45}We were a very happy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.49,0:28:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们住的村子也是这样\N{\fs45}We lived in a village like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.30,0:28:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像剑角村一样\N{\fs45}And like Daggerhorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.97,0:28:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们村也曾受狼人侵扰\N{\fs45}ours was plagued by a werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.40,0:28:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个月圆之夜  我和朋友们喝醉了\N{\fs45}One full moon, my friends and I got drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.31,0:28:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决定追捕它\N{\fs45}We decided to hunt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.14,0:28:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从没想过会找到它\N{\fs45}It never occurred to us that we might actually find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.91,0:28:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们竟然真的找到了\N{\fs45}but find it we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.68,0:28:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那畜生\N{\fs45}It ripped...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.49,0:28:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我最好的朋友撕成了两半\N{\fs45}my best friend in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.09,0:28:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那么一下\N{\fs45}Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.93,0:28:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后它扑向我\N{\fs45}And then it was on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我举起斧头砍啊砍\N{\fs45}I hacked and hacked at it with my axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.84,0:29:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然\N{\fs45}Suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.24,0:29:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不见了\N{\fs45}it was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.51,0:29:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我砍下了它的一只前爪\N{\fs45}I had cut off one of its front paws.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.91,0:29:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这是个不错的纪念品\N{\fs45}I thought it might make a clever souvenir,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.66,0:29:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就拿回了家\N{\fs45}and so l took it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.08,0:29:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果发现\N{\fs45}And there I found my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.65,0:29:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子手腕上缠着一块血淋淋的布\N{\fs45}...with a bloody rag wrapped around her wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.52,0:29:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再打开袋子一看\N{\fs45}And when I opened my sack...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.32,0:29:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人的爪子\N{\fs45}the werewolf's paw...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.16,0:29:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了\N{\fs45}was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.06,0:29:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取而代之的是这个\N{\fs45}This was in its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.67,0:29:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉女儿是狼人杀了她们的妈妈\N{\fs45}I told my girls the werewolf killed their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.05,0:29:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我骗了她们\N{\fs45}But that was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.75,0:29:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我杀了她\N{\fs45}I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.09,0:30:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人死后会变回人形\N{\fs45}When a werewolf dies, it returns to its human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.39,0:30:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这只是一只普通的灰狼\N{\fs45}That is just a common gray wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.90,0:30:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的狼人\N{\fs45}Your werewolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活得好好的\N{\fs45}is still very much alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.39,0:30:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是教廷庇护的三把银剑之一\N{\fs45}This is one of only three silver swords blessed by the Holy See.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.16,0:30:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能摸一下吗\N{\fs45}May I touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.73,0:30:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs45}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.57,0:30:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是危险时刻\N{\fs45}This is a very dangerous time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.54,0:30:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道血月意味着什么\N{\fs45}You all know what the Blood Moon means.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.17,0:30:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们完全不知道\N{\fs45}They have no idea what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.93,0:31:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是太阳系仪\N{\fs45}The orrery.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.40,0:31:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗红色行星每隔13年跟月球连成一线\N{\fs45}The red planet converges with the moon once every 13 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.24,0:31:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是产生新狼人的唯一时间\N{\fs45}This is the only time a new werewolf can be created.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.38,0:31:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在血月这一周\N{\fs45}During the week of the Blood Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.41,0:31:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要被狼人咬一口就会受到诅咒\N{\fs45}the werewolf may pass his curse on with a single bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.58,0:31:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一般的月圆之夜  狼人只能咬死你\N{\fs45}During a normal full moon, a wolf bite will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.52,0:31:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在血月时期\N{\fs45}But during a Blood Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.09,0:31:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的灵魂都无法幸免于难\N{\fs45}your very souls are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.59,0:31:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这三天  血月亏减之前\N{\fs45}Until the Blood Moon wanes in three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.70,0:31:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都不安全\N{\fs45}you will never truly be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.37,0:31:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在安全了\N{\fs45}We're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.09,0:31:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了狼人  捣了它的老巢\N{\fs45}I killed the wolf in its lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.57,0:31:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在格瑞摩尔山上的洞里\N{\fs45}The cave at Mount Grimmoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.47,0:32:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一开始就被这只畜生骗了\N{\fs45}You have been deceived by this beast from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.11,0:32:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们以为它住在格瑞摩尔\N{\fs45}It made you think it lived on Grimmoor...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.15,0:32:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你们就不会在最容易发现的地方找寻它\N{\fs45}so that you would not look for it in the most obvious place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.22,0:32:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人就住在这里\N{\fs45}The wolf lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.92,0:32:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在村里\N{\fs45}In this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.79,0:32:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你们中间\N{\fs45}Among you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.23,0:32:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的凶手可能是你的邻居\N{\fs45}The real killer could be your neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.93,0:32:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -你最好的朋友\N{\fs45}- What? - Your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.06,0:32:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至你的妻子\N{\fs45}Even your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.44,0:32:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-封锁全村  -你不能这样\N{\fs45}- Barricade the village. - You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.58,0:32:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把守每个出口  杀死狼人前谁都不准离开\N{\fs45}Post men at every gate! No one leaves until we kill the wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.08,0:32:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-遵命  -狼人已经死了\N{\fs45}- As you wish. - The wolf is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.92,0:32:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚  我们庆祝狂欢\N{\fs45}Tonight we celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.02,0:32:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs45}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.34,0:33:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  庆祝\N{\fs45}Go ahead. Celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.84,0:33:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走着瞧\N{\fs45}We'll see who is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.09,0:33:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人死啦\N{\fs45}The wolf is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.26,0:33:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面具摘了\N{\fs45}Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.92,0:33:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吸气  我吹气\N{\fs45}I'll huff, and I'll puff...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.75,0:33:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吹倒你的房子\N{\fs45}and I'll blow your house down!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.04,0:34:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小个子真好笑\N{\fs45}Laugh at the little man!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.36,0:34:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽  来跳舞啊\N{\fs45}Valerie, come dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.64,0:34:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吸气\N{\fs45}I'll huff...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.94,0:34:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吹气\N{\fs45}I'll puff...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.28,0:34:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吹倒你的房子\N{\fs45}and I'll blow your house down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.46,0:35:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍打拍打就干净了  我这样见教皇都行\N{\fs45}I'll just flick this off. I'll be fit to see the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.67,0:35:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs45}Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的好女儿\N{\fs45}You're my good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.31,0:35:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs45}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.41,0:35:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  现在回家好吗\N{\fs45}I know. Just go home now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.27,0:35:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逗你玩\N{\fs45}Tricked you. Ha-ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.41,0:35:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错\N{\fs45}Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.78,0:35:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪儿学的\N{\fs45}Where did you learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.28,0:35:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德\N{\fs45}Claude.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.82,0:36:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德  回去参加派对吧\N{\fs45}Claude, come back to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.43,0:36:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来罗丝的裙下之臣又多了一个\N{\fs45}Looks like Rose has a new conquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.95,0:36:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  普鲁登斯\N{\fs45}Come on, Prudence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.28,0:37:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丢下了我们\N{\fs45}You left us!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.08,0:37:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点  朋友\N{\fs45}Take it easy, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.28,0:37:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我们不该分头行动  但你丢下了我们\N{\fs45}I said we should stick together and you left us,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.58,0:37:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样我父亲才死的\N{\fs45}and my father is dead because of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.48,0:37:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样\N{\fs45}Please don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.96,0:37:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰她  不然我砍掉你的手\N{\fs45}Keep your hands off her or I'll cut them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.26,0:37:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fs45}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.45,0:38:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟着我\N{\fs45}Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.12,0:38:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么\N{\fs45}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.52,0:38:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要我怎样  你才能不跟着我\N{\fs45}What do I have to do to make you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.66,0:38:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你  彼得\N{\fs45}I love you, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.49,0:38:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟罗丝怎么回事\N{\fs45}What are you doing with Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.47,0:38:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不喜欢她\N{\fs45}You don't even like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.77,0:38:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用喜欢她  我就能从她身上得到我想要的\N{\fs45}I don't have to like her to get what I want from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.37,0:38:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会撒谎\N{\fs45}You're a terrible liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.37,0:38:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的感觉跟我一样\N{\fs45}I know you feel like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.71,0:38:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你正欲火焚身\N{\fs45}I know you're burning inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.64,0:38:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远也给不了你这种东西\N{\fs45}I'll never be able to give you anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.08,0:38:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我在意亨利的钱吗\N{\fs45}Think I care about Henry's money?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.71,0:38:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟他才有未来\N{\fs45}You have a future with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.83,0:38:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你自毁幸福\N{\fs45}I'm not gonna let you ruin that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.88,0:38:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈找你谈过是吗\N{\fs45}Did my mother get to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.59,0:38:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽  我配不上你\N{\fs45}Valerie, I'm wrong for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.33,0:38:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fs45}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.24,0:39:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把你吃个一干二净\N{\fs45}I could eat you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.19,0:40:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想要我吗\N{\fs45}Don't you want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.41,0:40:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿   彼得\N{\fs45}Hey, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.91,0:40:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  帮个忙\N{\fs45}Come on, give us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.59,0:40:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想跟你在一起\N{\fs45}The only life I want is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.97,0:41:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚去哪儿了\N{\fs45}So where did you disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.84,0:41:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道谷仓里那些干草有多柔软吗\N{\fs45}You know all that soft hay in the granary?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.52,0:41:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快跑  -去教堂\N{\fs45}- Run! - Get to the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.16,0:41:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-彼得  -快走\N{\fs45}-Peter! - Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.87,0:41:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德\N{\fs45}Claude!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.64,0:41:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的死期到了  畜生\N{\fs45}You will die now, beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.15,0:42:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人无法踏足圣地\N{\fs45}The wolf can't cross onto holy ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.69,0:42:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去教堂\N{\fs45}Get to the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.75,0:42:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去教堂\N{\fs45}The church!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.02,0:42:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德\N{\fs45}Claude!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.56,0:42:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  绑住它\N{\fs45}Now! Rope it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.81,0:42:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖住它\N{\fs45}Hold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.11,0:42:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德\N{\fs45}Claude!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.35,0:42:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-它太强了  -上帝更强\N{\fs45}- It's strong. - God is stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.26,0:42:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝更强\N{\fs45}God is stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.72,0:43:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我警告过你们\N{\fs45}I warned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.96,0:43:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告过你们\N{\fs45}I warned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.33,0:43:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的狼人还活着\N{\fs45}Your werewolf is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.90,0:43:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到它\N{\fs45}Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.40,0:43:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到它\N{\fs45}Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.41,0:43:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到它\N{\fs45}Find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.75,0:43:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里\N{\fs45}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.41,0:44:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不出我的手掌心\N{\fs45}You can't escape from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.02,0:44:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  你会说话\N{\fs45}Oh, my God. You can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.42,0:44:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能\N{\fs45}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.82,0:44:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你听得懂我的话  就这么简单  瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}You understand me. That's all that matters, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.29,0:44:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我的名字\N{\fs45}You know my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.79,0:44:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fs45}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.80,0:44:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的眼睛  深褐色\N{\fs45}Human eyes, dark brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.47,0:44:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很了解你\N{\fs45}I know you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.87,0:44:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想离开这个村子\N{\fs45}You dream of leaving this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.18,0:44:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吧\N{\fs45}Let me take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.35,0:44:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我是一样的\N{\fs45}You and I are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.22,0:44:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我才不像你  杀人凶手\N{\fs45}No, I'm nothing like you. You're a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.75,0:45:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是凶手  不是吗\N{\fs45}You're a killer too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.96,0:45:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那只兔子吗  瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}What happened to the rabbit, Valerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.86,0:45:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了它\N{\fs45}I killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.53,0:45:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  所以跟我走吧\N{\fs45}I know. So come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.37,0:45:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs45}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.57,0:45:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那街上将会血流成河  先从她开始\N{\fs45}Then the streets will run red with blood. Starting with hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.34,0:45:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs45}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.48,0:45:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父会阻止你的\N{\fs45}Father Solomon will stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.25,0:45:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父也会像其他人一样必死无疑\N{\fs45}Father Solomon will die like the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.22,0:45:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血月结束前我还会回来找你\N{\fs45}I'm coming back for you before the Blood Moon wanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.49,0:45:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里  放箭\N{\fs45}There! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.01,0:45:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚跟狼人说话了\N{\fs45}You talked to the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.61,0:45:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是它跟我们说话\N{\fs45}No, it talked to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.24,0:45:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那只是狼嚎\N{\fs45}No, it growled.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.68,0:46:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你听到它跟你说话了吗\N{\fs45}Wait, you heard it talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.65,0:46:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会说我是巫婆  别告诉别人\N{\fs45}They'll call me a witch. Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.95,0:46:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  当然不会\N{\fs45}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.69,0:46:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到圣地上来\N{\fs45}Get inside onto holy ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.31,0:46:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我要去找我弟弟\N{\fs45}Wait, I have to find my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.76,0:46:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还有我的家人  -日出之前不准离开\N{\fs45}- And my family. - No one leaves until sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.62,0:46:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-进去  -这是为了你们自己的安全\N{\fs45}- Go. - For your own safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.82,0:46:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前怀疑您是我们的不对  神父\N{\fs45}We were wrong to have doubted you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.52,0:46:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过这么强的猛兽\N{\fs45}I've never seen a beast as strong as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.19,0:46:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此强大的生物\N{\fs45}A creature this powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.74,0:46:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定血统纯正  由来已久了\N{\fs45}must come from a long uninterrupted bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.50,0:46:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一代更比一代强\N{\fs45}Each generation more potent than the one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.61,0:47:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须找到它的人形\N{\fs45}We must find it in its human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.14,0:47:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么找  谁都有可能\N{\fs45}But how? It could be any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.65,0:47:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一眼就能发现  它就活不了这么久\N{\fs45}It hasn't survived this long by being obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.81,0:47:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细找\N{\fs45}Look everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.12,0:47:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种标记\N{\fs45}Look for the signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.66,0:47:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤僻\N{\fs45}Isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.36,0:47:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫术\N{\fs45}Witchcraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.49,0:47:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑魔法\N{\fs45}The black arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.46,0:47:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异常行为\N{\fs45}Abnormal behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.67,0:47:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的气味\N{\fs45}Strange smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.30,0:47:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一家都要搜查\N{\fs45}Your homes will be searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.54,0:47:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的秘密无处可藏\N{\fs45}Your secrets brought to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.01,0:47:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你若无辜  则无需害怕\N{\fs45}If you are innocent, you have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.85,0:47:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若有罪\N{\fs45}But if you are guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.62,0:47:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向万能的上帝发誓\N{\fs45}I swear by Almighty God...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.22,0:47:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会消灭你\N{\fs45}you will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.26,0:47:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还活着\N{\fs45}He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.23,0:47:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我水\N{\fs45}Bring me water!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.83,0:47:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs45}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.51,0:48:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是血月  所以他必须\N{\fs45}It's a Blood Moon. So he must--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.11,0:48:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我弟弟\N{\fs45}He's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.00,0:48:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被咬过的人就是受了诅咒\N{\fs45}A man bitten... is a man cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.48,0:49:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽  开开门\N{\fs45}Valerie, open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.96,0:49:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们处境危险\N{\fs45}We're all in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.27,0:49:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得马上离开\N{\fs45}So we've gotta leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.22,0:49:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吧\N{\fs45}Come away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.23,0:49:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吧\N{\fs45}Come away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.27,0:49:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吧\N{\fs45}Come away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.37,0:49:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾好东西  我们必须马上走\N{\fs45}Get your things. We have to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.34,0:49:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能跟你走  彼得\N{\fs45}I can't go with you, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.88,0:49:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs45}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.48,0:49:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs45}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.20,0:50:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\fs45}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.71,0:50:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会没事的\N{\fs45}She's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.41,0:50:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人抓伤了她\N{\fs45}The wolf just scratched her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.29,0:50:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是咬伤\N{\fs45}That's not a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.08,0:50:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她的头抬起来  瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Lift her head, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.49,0:50:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  喝了它  亲爱的\N{\fs45}Here. Drink this, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.56,0:50:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有助于睡眠\N{\fs45}It'll help you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.37,0:50:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\fs45}You sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.15,0:51:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  亲爱的\N{\fs45}What is it, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.32,0:51:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs45}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.53,0:51:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人\N{\fs45}The wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.46,0:51:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它跟我说话了\N{\fs45}It talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.43,0:51:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能听懂它的话\N{\fs45}And you understood it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.97,0:51:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像能听懂你的话一样\N{\fs45}As clearly as I understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.34,0:51:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事你告诉过别人吗\N{\fs45}Have you told anyone else about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.44,0:51:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有罗克珊知道  但她不会告诉别人\N{\fs45}Only Roxanne knows, but she won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.11,0:51:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她甚至都不愿跟我说这事\N{\fs45}She won't even talk to me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.48,0:51:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它没有杀你\N{\fs45}It chose not to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.12,0:51:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想它希望我活着\N{\fs45}I think it wants me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.37,0:52:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -再给我拿一条绷带\N{\fs45}- No. - Bring me another bandage.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.38,0:52:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs45}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.12,0:52:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去打点清水\N{\fs45}I have to get clean water.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.89,0:52:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德回家了吗\N{\fs45}Has Claude come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.83,0:52:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人见过他\N{\fs45}Nobody's seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.67,0:52:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边来  回屋里去  快点\N{\fs45}There you go, back inside. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.64,0:52:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得让我们进去\N{\fs45}You have to let us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.35,0:52:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见你跟彼得在一起\N{\fs45}I saw you with Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.15,0:52:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你不希望我那样\N{\fs45}I know you don't want me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.46,0:52:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会逼你嫁给我\N{\fs45}I'm not gonna force you to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.26,0:52:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会中止婚约\N{\fs45}I'm gonna break off the engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.92,0:53:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  亨利\N{\fs45}I'm sorry, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.33,0:53:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fs45}That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.63,0:53:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父\N{\fs45}Father Solomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.49,0:53:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发现有人藏在塔里\N{\fs45}We found someone hiding in the tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.43,0:53:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs45}Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.08,0:53:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是我弟弟  别碰他  -把他弄下来\N{\fs45}- It's my brother! Don't touch him! - Get him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.68,0:53:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-审问他  -他不是狼人\N{\fs45}-Interrogate him! - He's not the wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.71,0:53:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他\N{\fs45}Look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.35,0:53:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他话都说不清  他在跟魔鬼交流\N{\fs45}His speech is twisted. He communes with demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.72,0:53:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他弄下来  马上\N{\fs45}Get him down! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.65,0:53:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他什么都没干\N{\fs45}He hasn't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.92,0:53:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他研究巫术的证据\N{\fs45}This is proof that he studies the black arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.96,0:54:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个巫师\N{\fs45}He's a conjurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.16,0:54:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我了解他  -比我了解我妻子还清楚吗\N{\fs45}- I know him. - Better than I knew my own wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.63,0:54:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不知道一个人有多少能耐\N{\fs45}You never know what someone is capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.37,0:54:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他弄下来  快点\N{\fs45}Get him down! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.47,0:54:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我狼人的名字\N{\fs45}Give me the name of the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.81,0:54:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我名字\N{\fs45}Give me the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.78,0:54:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我\N{\fs45}Tell me the name!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.59,0:55:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是罗马人发明的\N{\fs45}The Romans invented this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.10,0:55:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来发掘真相的精妙方法\N{\fs45}An ingenious system for extracting the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.24,0:55:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么能告诉你名字呢\N{\fs45}How can he give you a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.05,0:55:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子话都不会说\N{\fs45}The boy can barely speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.04,0:55:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听听他如何歌颂对撒旦的爱吧\N{\fs45}Listen to how he sings of his love of Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.98,0:55:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这么做也是出于好意\N{\fs45}We do this for the greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.88,0:55:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么好处\N{\fs45}What's the good in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.32,0:55:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了我妻子是为了保护我的孩子\N{\fs45}I killed my wife to protect my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.69,0:55:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候  我们顺行天意的办法不尽人意\N{\fs45}Our methods of pleasing God are sometimes flawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.46,0:55:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好能接受它\N{\fs45}You had best develop a stomach for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.53,0:56:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说有要事\N{\fs45}She says it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.43,0:56:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为释放我弟弟来跟你讲条件的\N{\fs45}I've come to bargain for the release of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.37,0:56:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银指甲\N{\fs45}Silver fingernails.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.81,0:56:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样才能杀死狼人\N{\fs45}To kill a werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.18,0:56:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去\N{\fs45}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.62,0:56:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  除了钱我还有别的\N{\fs45}Please, I have more than money to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.27,0:56:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过去\N{\fs45}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.78,0:57:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  走吧\N{\fs45}Enough. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.25,0:57:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  求你了  我还有别的\N{\fs45}Wait, please. I have something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.09,0:57:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放了我弟弟  我告诉你谁是巫女\N{\fs45}Spare my brother and I'll give you the name of a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.16,0:57:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs45}Now, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.83,0:57:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还有点价值\N{\fs45}is worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.67,0:57:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你跟我说的告诉他们\N{\fs45}Tell them what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.91,0:57:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能爬上最高的树\N{\fs45}She can climb the tallest trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.82,0:57:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她比别的女孩儿跑得都快\N{\fs45}She can run faster than all the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.38,0:57:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她身穿红色的斗篷  那是魔鬼的颜色\N{\fs45}She wears a red cloak. The devil's color.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.55,0:57:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道  那件斗篷是我做的\N{\fs45}That's nonsense. I made that cloak.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.09,0:57:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静  继续说\N{\fs45}Silence! Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.26,0:57:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能跟狼人说话\N{\fs45}And she can talk to werewolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.60,0:58:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到的  亲眼所见\N{\fs45}I've seen it. With my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.14,0:58:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你否认吗\N{\fs45}Do you deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.56,0:58:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不否认\N{\fs45}No, I don't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.32,0:58:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们谈了些什么\N{\fs45}And what was the nature of this conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.22,0:58:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它说只要我跟它走  就不再骚扰剑角村\N{\fs45}It promised to leave Daggerhorn in peace as long as I go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.53,0:58:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人是村子里某个想要得到你的人  瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}The wolf is someone in this village who wants you, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.13,0:58:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是谁吗\N{\fs45}Do you know who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.00,0:58:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是换做我  我会努力想想\N{\fs45}I'd think very hard if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.74,0:58:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fs45}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.35,0:58:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我是谁\N{\fs45}Tell me who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.88,0:58:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我名字\N{\fs45}Give me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.99,0:59:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它想要的是她  不是你们\N{\fs45}It wants her, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.76,0:59:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要想安保自身\N{\fs45}If you wish to save yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.56,0:59:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要就把它想要的给它就行\N{\fs45}simply give it what it wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.73,0:59:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能把她交给那狼人\N{\fs45}You can't give her to the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.03,0:59:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是人类献祭\N{\fs45}That's human sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.63,0:59:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都牺牲了太多\N{\fs45}We've all made sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.74,0:59:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判结束  都回家去吧\N{\fs45}The trial is over. Go back to your homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.94,0:59:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了都回家去  所有人\N{\fs45}I said go home. All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.35,0:59:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你在乎她呢\N{\fs45}I thought you cared about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.87,0:59:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在乎她\N{\fs45}I do care.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.92,0:59:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很在乎\N{\fs45}I do care.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.89,0:59:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得想个好办法\N{\fs45}I'm trying to be smart about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.53,0:59:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到谷仓去\N{\fs45}Go to the granary.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.70,0:59:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去救她吗\N{\fs45}You're gonna try and rescue her?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.10,0:59:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我要帮忙\N{\fs45}Well, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.87,0:59:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没绝望到要你帮忙\N{\fs45}I'm not that desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.14,0:59:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那你的计划是什么\N{\fs45}Oh, really? Then what's your plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.88,0:59:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  你连计划都没有\N{\fs45}See, you don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.15,0:59:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经见过那些锁了\N{\fs45}Look, you've seen those locks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.08,1:00:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个铺子还有工具  你需要我\N{\fs45}I've got a shop and I've got tools. You need me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.02,1:00:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs45}Okay. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.09,1:00:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  如果你就是狼人\N{\fs45}But if you're the wolf,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.16,1:00:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把你的头砍下来\N{\fs45}I'm gonna chop your head off.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.83,1:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样\N{\fs45}I will do the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.07,1:00:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs45}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.74,1:00:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家去吧\N{\fs45}Go home!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.64,1:00:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟在哪里\N{\fs45}Where's my brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.43,1:00:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父说你们会放了他\N{\fs45}Father Solomon told me you'd release him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.08,1:00:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经放了\N{\fs45}We did.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.19,1:01:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶\N{\fs45}Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.47,1:01:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有面包和毯子\N{\fs45}Bread. Blanket.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.87,1:01:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要别的吗\N{\fs45}Do you need anything else?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.51,1:01:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你别用到那把刀\N{\fs45}I do not want you to use that knife.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.55,1:01:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们必须找到狼人  -在日落之前吗\N{\fs45}- We have to find the wolf. - By sundown?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.41,1:01:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  狼人想要的是你\N{\fs45}Listen, the wolf wants you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.73,1:01:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它先杀了你姐姐\N{\fs45}But first it killed your sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.42,1:01:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不知道\N{\fs45}No. I didn't know it,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.02,1:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是露西爱上了亨利\N{\fs45}but Lucie was in love with Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.53,1:01:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当她发现我订了婚\N{\fs45}And when she found out about my engagement...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.20,1:01:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就她把自己交给了狼人\N{\fs45}...she gave herself to the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.67,1:01:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  露西不会那么做\N{\fs45}No. Lucie wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.57,1:02:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-时间到了  -但她可能是对亨利有所回应\N{\fs45}- Your time is up. - But she might have responded to Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.94,1:02:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把这些交给她\N{\fs45}Please see that she gets that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.38,1:02:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货\N{\fs45}Oaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.70,1:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞泽尔\N{\fs45}Cesaire.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.54,1:02:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会救回你的女儿  然后跟她结婚\N{\fs45}I'm gonna save your daughter. And then I intend to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.17,1:02:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望得到你的祝福\N{\fs45}I'd like your blessing in this,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.55,1:02:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有祝福也没关系\N{\fs45}but I can live without it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.18,1:02:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做点什么\N{\fs45}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.46,1:02:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们关门了\N{\fs45}We're closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.13,1:03:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fs45}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.97,1:03:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  亨利\N{\fs45}Hello, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.93,1:03:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我给你带了些饼干  -谢谢\N{\fs45}- I brought you some biscuits. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.77,1:03:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想谢谢你早上说的那些\N{\fs45}I just wanna thank you for speaking up this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.88,1:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来试试吧\N{\fs45}Here, try some.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.15,1:03:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs45}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.62,1:03:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很勇敢\N{\fs45}That was very brave of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.42,1:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是实话实说\N{\fs45}I said what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.02,1:03:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs45}You know...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.16,1:03:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你明白\N{\fs45}...I want you to know you're
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.13,1:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并没有义务维护瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}under no obligation to stand up for Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.93,1:03:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不再是她的未婚夫\N{\fs45}You're no longer engaged to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.70,1:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她爱上了别人\N{\fs45}She's in love with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.53,1:03:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不意味着我就不能再关心她\N{\fs45}That doesn't mean I've stopped caring about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.30,1:03:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想露西也是这样对你的\N{\fs45}I imagine that's just how Lucie felt about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.31,1:03:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有一点喜欢我\N{\fs45}She had a crush on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.91,1:03:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是喜欢\N{\fs45}Oh, more than a crush.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.07,1:03:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她会为了你做任何事\N{\fs45}I think she would have done absolutely anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.61,1:03:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使要她在狼人出没的夜晚跟你见面\N{\fs45}Even agree to meet you on a wolf night
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.72,1:03:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你说她就会去\N{\fs45}if you asked her to.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.63,1:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思\N{\fs45}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.53,1:04:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我是狼人吗\N{\fs45}Do you think I'm the wolf?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.51,1:04:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在指责我是凶手吗\N{\fs45}Are you accusing me of murder?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.14,1:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没指责你什么\N{\fs45}I'm not accusing you of anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.67,1:04:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想找出真相\N{\fs45}I just want to find out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.15,1:04:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你\N{\fs45}It's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.68,1:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  是你  我能在你身上闻到那味道\N{\fs45}My god, it's you. I can smell it on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.59,1:04:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在我身上闻到什么味道了\N{\fs45}Heh. What can you smell on me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.65,1:04:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲死的那晚\N{\fs45}The night my father died,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.28,1:04:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闻到了狼人的味道\N{\fs45}I could smell the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.46,1:04:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是一种很浓的麝香味\N{\fs45}It was like a deep musk.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.56,1:04:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在你身上也闻到了这种味道\N{\fs45}And I can smell it all over you right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.50,1:04:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大晚上的  独自一人\N{\fs45}What do you do out there in that cabin
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.62,1:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那小屋里做什么\N{\fs45}all by yourself in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.17,1:04:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西死的那晚\N{\fs45}On the night that Lucie died?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.50,1:04:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道  对吧\N{\fs45}You don't know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.44,1:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在做什么\N{\fs45}I know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.17,1:04:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你把事情推到我身上\N{\fs45}And I'm not gonna let you turn this on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.83,1:05:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我们走\N{\fs45}You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.35,1:06:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做\N{\fs45}I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.26,1:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一\N{\fs45}Just a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.82,1:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父不想巫女的家人惹什么麻烦\N{\fs45}Father Solomon doesn't want any trouble from the witch's family.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.00,1:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候穿上你妖女的袍子了\N{\fs45}It's time to put on your harlot's robe.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.32,1:06:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.53,1:06:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽了最大的努力保护你们\N{\fs45}I did my best to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.13,1:06:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和露西\N{\fs45}You and Lucie.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.53,1:06:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  爸爸\N{\fs45}I know, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.94,1:07:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你教我们要坚强\N{\fs45}You taught us to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.35,1:07:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门神父设计了这个面具  好让大家羞辱我\N{\fs45}Father Solomon had designed the mask for public disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.79,1:07:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是我的朋友也盯着我批判我\N{\fs45}And even my friends stared, judging me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.40,1:07:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fs45}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.83,1:07:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们是对的呢\N{\fs45}What if they were right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.77,1:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许狼人知道些我所不知的\N{\fs45}Maybe the wolf knew something I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.80,1:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我的内心的确藏有黑暗的东西\N{\fs45}Maybe there was something dark inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.57,1:07:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都回家去吧\N{\fs45}You should all go home!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.19,1:07:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}I'm so sorry, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.85,1:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到事情会这样\N{\fs45}I didn't mean for this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.29,1:07:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福你  亲爱的\N{\fs45}Bless you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.23,1:08:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯\N{\fs45}Prudence.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.57,1:08:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.17,1:08:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗克珊让我转告说她很抱歉\N{\fs45}Roxanne wanted me to tell you how sorry she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.07,1:08:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那么说是为了救她弟弟\N{\fs45}She said those things to save her brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.25,1:08:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  告诉她我不怪她\N{\fs45}I know. Tell her that I forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.71,1:08:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\fs45}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.92,1:08:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想说\N{\fs45}But I wanted to say....
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.08,1:08:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道该说什么\N{\fs45}I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.45,1:08:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不用说了\N{\fs45}But you don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.16,1:08:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想说\N{\fs45}But I want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.16,1:08:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你知道\N{\fs45}I want you to know that...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.56,1:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许骗得了罗克珊\N{\fs45}...you may have fooled Roxanne...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.43,1:08:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你骗不了我\N{\fs45}...but you don't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.40,1:08:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不会了\N{\fs45}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.24,1:08:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是那么好\N{\fs45}You were always too good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.70,1:08:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么漂亮\N{\fs45}Too pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.94,1:08:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么完美\N{\fs45}Too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.48,1:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你欺骗了我们\N{\fs45}You tricked us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.48,1:08:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你要得到应有的惩罚\N{\fs45}Now you're gonna get what you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.12,1:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯  我想你该走了\N{\fs45}Prudence, I think you should go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.02,1:09:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs45}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.43,1:09:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会太久的\N{\fs45}It won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.90,1:09:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人马上就来了\N{\fs45}The wolf is coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.20,1:09:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人就住在这里\N{\fs45}The wolf lives here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.31,1:09:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的邻居  你最好的朋友\N{\fs45}Your neighbor. Your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.77,1:09:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至可能是你的妻子\N{\fs45}Even your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.04,1:09:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很漂亮\N{\fs45}You're the pretty one.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.48,1:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我会把你吃个一干二净  -你会快乐起来的\N{\fs45}- I could eat you up. - You will be happy again.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.95,1:09:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的眼睛  深褐色\N{\fs45}Human eyes, dark brown.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.72,1:09:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很了解你\N{\fs45}I know you well.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.50,1:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道怎么杀老虎吗  奥古斯特神父\N{\fs45}Do you know how you kill a tiger, Father Auguste?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.91,1:09:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拴上最好的山羊做诱饵\N{\fs45}You tie out your best goat...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.71,1:09:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后等待\N{\fs45}and wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.04,1:10:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着火了\N{\fs45}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.71,1:10:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快救火\N{\fs45}Put it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.75,1:11:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去\N{\fs45}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.33,1:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你离开这里\N{\fs45}I'm gonna get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.18,1:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火势太大\N{\fs45}It's too much!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.04,1:12:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fs45}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.79,1:12:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那  他上钩了  放箭\N{\fs45}There! He's taken the bait! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.46,1:12:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  那不是狼人\N{\fs45}Wait, that's not the wolf!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.96,1:12:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在帮巫女\N{\fs45}He's aiding a witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.76,1:12:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-放箭  -不要\N{\fs45}- Fire! - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.77,1:12:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs45}Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.68,1:12:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑\N{\fs45}Run.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.20,1:13:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他放的火\N{\fs45}This one started the fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.70,1:13:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他关起来  关到铜象里去\N{\fs45}Lock him up. In the elephant!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.70,1:13:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-走  -带走\N{\fs45}- Go! - Move it!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.90,1:13:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫女已经跑了\N{\fs45}The witch has escaped!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.96,1:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来集合  找出巫女\N{\fs45}Get over here! Find the witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.86,1:13:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  彼得带了马和我们汇合\N{\fs45}Come on, Peter's meeting us with the horses.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.77,1:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.84,1:13:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.78,1:13:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得在哪\N{\fs45}Where's Peter?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.02,1:13:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs45}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.12,1:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他会来\N{\fs45}He said he'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.99,1:14:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他没出现\N{\fs45}If he doesn't show...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.26,1:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我带你走\N{\fs45}I'm gonna take you away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.83,1:14:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我带你走吧\N{\fs45}Let me take you away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.83,1:14:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我是狼人吗\N{\fs45}Do you think I'm the wolf?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.17,1:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出巫女\N{\fs45}Find the witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.98,1:14:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  快\N{\fs45}Come on! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.45,1:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走\N{\fs45}Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.89,1:14:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边\N{\fs45}That way!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.15,1:14:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该去教堂\N{\fs45}We should go to the church.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.49,1:14:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人不能踏入圣地\N{\fs45}The wolf can't cross onto holy ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.13,1:14:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分人跟我走  这边  我们走\N{\fs45}Some with me! This way! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.01,1:14:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到那边有声音\N{\fs45}I heard something over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.65,1:14:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在这  快追\N{\fs45}They're in here! After them!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.29,1:15:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.16,1:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利  亨利\N{\fs45}Henry. Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.63,1:15:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走  瓦莱丽  走\N{\fs45}Go. Valerie, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.83,1:15:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不会丢下你的\N{\fs45}No. I'm not leaving you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.54,1:15:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们请求庇护\N{\fs45}We claim sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.76,1:15:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没进入圣地呢\N{\fs45}You are not on holy ground yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.22,1:15:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...\N{\fs45}This...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.15,1:15:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的\N{\fs45}belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.84,1:16:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要她活命\N{\fs45}You want her alive?!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.78,1:16:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了它\N{\fs45}Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.86,1:16:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.40,1:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨出这道门  不然我就灭了这个村子\N{\fs45}Step across the gate, or I'll destroy this village.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.10,1:16:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁太阳还没升起  跟我走\N{\fs45}Come with me before the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.81,1:16:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做决定吧\N{\fs45}Make your decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.51,1:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你毁了我的家园\N{\fs45}I won't let you destroy my home.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.65,1:16:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我跟你走  -不要  瓦莱丽  不\N{\fs45}- I'll go with you. - Don't! Valerie. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.45,1:16:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你保证不伤害他们\N{\fs45}If you promise to leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.56,1:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不会让你为了我们而牺牲自己\N{\fs45}No. I won't let you sacrifice yourself for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.26,1:16:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也不会  -我也不会\N{\fs45}- Nor will I.  - Nor will l.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.96,1:16:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我支持瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}I stand by Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.12,1:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你躲不过我的\N{\fs45}You can't hide from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.02,1:17:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这巫女还是要被烧死\N{\fs45}The witch will still burn!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.56,1:17:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血月之下\N{\fs45}Under the Blood Moon...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.23,1:17:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被咬过的人就是受了诅咒\N{\fs45}A man bitten is a man cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.77,1:17:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子将成为孤儿\N{\fs45}My children will be orphaned.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.88,1:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的弟弟\N{\fs45}My brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.38,1:17:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有孩子\N{\fs45}had children too.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.71,1:17:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并无恶意\N{\fs45}I meant only to serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.72,1:17:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想保护我们远离黑暗\N{\fs45}To protect us from darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.11,1:18:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血月之下\N{\fs45}Under the Blood Moon...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.48,1:18:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被咬过的人就是受了诅咒\N{\fs45}A man bitten is a man cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.49,1:18:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得在哪\N{\fs45}Where's Peter?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.96,1:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得在哪\N{\fs45}Where's Peter?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.70,1:19:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶\N{\fs45}Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.64,1:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛好大\N{\fs45}What big eyes you have.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.34,1:19:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了把你看得更清楚啊  宝贝\N{\fs45}The better to see you with, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.98,1:19:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  你的耳朵好大\N{\fs45}Grandmother, what big ears you have.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.02,1:19:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了听清楚你说的话啊  宝贝\N{\fs45}The better to hear you with, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.43,1:19:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的牙齿也好大\N{\fs45}What big teeth you have.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.13,1:19:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样更方便吃掉你啊  宝贝\N{\fs45}The better to eat you with, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.82,1:20:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽  你怎么起床了\N{\fs45}Valerie. What are you doing out of bed?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.62,1:20:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很担心\N{\fs45}I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.30,1:20:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好多了\N{\fs45}It looks much better.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.41,1:20:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿\N{\fs45}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.68,1:20:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶家  我想她有危险\N{\fs45}To Grandmother's. I think she's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.72,1:21:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁狼人的足迹还没被风雪掩盖\N{\fs45}We're going after the wolf
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.34,1:21:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在就去找它\N{\fs45}before the storm can cover its tracks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.85,1:21:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它还会变回人形  然后我们就能杀掉它\N{\fs45}It'll be human again and we can finally kill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.36,1:21:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我...\N{\fs45}And I have....
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.59,1:21:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  告诉我\N{\fs45}What? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.60,1:21:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得还是下落不明\N{\fs45}Peter is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.17,1:21:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽我所能\N{\fs45}I'll do what I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.10,1:21:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万要小心\N{\fs45}Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.78,1:22:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.22,1:22:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地你一切都好\N{\fs45}Thank God you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.23,1:22:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\fs45}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.50,1:22:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我整晚都被关在那铜象里\N{\fs45}I was trapped in that brazen beast all night.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.34,1:22:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于逃了出来\N{\fs45}I finally broke out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.21,1:22:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠近我\N{\fs45}Don't come near me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.67,1:22:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Valerie, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.04,1:22:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不相信我吗\N{\fs45}You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.78,1:22:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会伤害你\N{\fs45}I'll hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.79,1:22:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你不会的\N{\fs45}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.59,1:22:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来\N{\fs45}Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.55,1:23:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶\N{\fs45}Grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.03,1:23:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  你还好吗\N{\fs45}Grandmother, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.23,1:23:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了个噩梦\N{\fs45}I had a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.53,1:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好\N{\fs45}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.77,1:23:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚醒来\N{\fs45}I just woke up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.87,1:23:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是饿了  可以喝点汤\N{\fs45}There's some soup if you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.42,1:23:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得狼人在这附近\N{\fs45}I think the wolf is out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.32,1:23:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  亲爱的  这里很安全\N{\fs45}It's all right, darling. We're safe in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.25,1:24:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧  记住\N{\fs45}Eat up. Remember
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.62,1:24:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-面包可以缓解忧伤  -缓解忧伤\N{\fs45}- "All sorrows are less with bread."  - "Less with bread".
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.23,1:24:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\fs45}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.40,1:24:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它吃光  亲爱的\N{\fs45}Eat up, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.93,1:24:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs45}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.15,1:24:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  你在这儿干嘛\N{\fs45}Father, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.02,1:24:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶呢\N{\fs45}Where's Grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.29,1:24:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我别无选择\N{\fs45}I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.79,1:24:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她终于意识到了我是谁\N{\fs45}She finally realized what I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.37,1:24:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能这么做\N{\fs45}How could you do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.41,1:24:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\fs45}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.81,1:24:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\fs45}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.88,1:25:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Oh, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.25,1:25:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直不受尊重\N{\fs45}I've been so disrespected.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.72,1:25:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的付出得不到应有的回报\N{\fs45}I've settled for far less than I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.84,1:25:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是\N{\fs45}So
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.62,1:25:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定离开\N{\fs45}I decided I'd leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.20,1:25:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去城里\N{\fs45}For the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.94,1:25:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是更好的猎场\N{\fs45}For richer hunting grounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.77,1:25:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不直接离开\N{\fs45}Why didn't you just leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.64,1:25:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我爱你们  我的女儿们\N{\fs45}Because I loved you girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.78,1:25:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你们和我一起走\N{\fs45}I wanted you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.71,1:25:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但你必须等到血月的时候  -没错\N{\fs45}- But you had to wait for the Blood Moon. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.42,1:25:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据常理\N{\fs45}By birthright...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.12,1:25:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼物应先由我的大女儿获得\N{\fs45}the gift would go first to my eldest daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.79,1:25:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我伪造了一封信\N{\fs45}So I forged a letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.53,1:25:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当我试图跟她对话的时候\N{\fs45}But when I tried to speak to her--
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.49,1:25:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利不会来了  露西\N{\fs45}Henry's not coming, Lucie.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.30,1:25:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她听不懂我说的话\N{\fs45}--she didn't understand me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.63,1:25:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子  流着我狼人血液的孩子\N{\fs45}Any offspring of mine with my wolf blood
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.90,1:25:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都应该能听懂\N{\fs45}would've been able to do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.71,1:26:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都真相大白了\N{\fs45}And then it all made sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.98,1:26:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西不可能是我的女儿\N{\fs45}Lucie couldn't be my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.18,1:26:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈骗了我\N{\fs45}Your mother lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.35,1:26:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早就知道  对吧\N{\fs45}But you knew that already, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.28,1:26:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些年来我一直小心谨慎\N{\fs45}After all these years of being so clever and so careful,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.41,1:26:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是失控了\N{\fs45}I just lost control.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.76,1:26:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对不起露西\N{\fs45}I'm sorry for Lucie.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.02,1:26:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你报复了妈妈\N{\fs45}You took revenge on mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.09,1:26:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有她的情人\N{\fs45}And her lover.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.07,1:26:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚  亨利闻出了狼人的气味\N{\fs45}Henry smelled the wolf that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.50,1:26:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也是\N{\fs45}And then again yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.27,1:26:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他以为这气味来自你奶奶\N{\fs45}He thought the smell came from your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.88,1:26:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她伴着这气味过了一辈子\N{\fs45}But she had lived with that smell her whole life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.49,1:26:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道  我的父亲也是狼人\N{\fs45}You see, my father was a wolf too.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.19,1:26:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他衣服上还留着那股味道\N{\fs45}The smell remained on his clothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.93,1:26:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到母亲临死前\N{\fs45}Mother never knew what it meant...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.02,1:26:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她才知道这意味着什么\N{\fs45}till the moment she died.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.74,1:27:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很爱她\N{\fs45}I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.94,1:27:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和露西  我从没想过要伤害她们\N{\fs45}Her and Lucie both. I never wanted to hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.91,1:27:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦莱丽  跟我一起走吧\N{\fs45}Valerie, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.38,1:27:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是血月的最后一天\N{\fs45}It's the last day of the Blood Moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.95,1:27:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要咬一下  你就会和我一样\N{\fs45}One bite, and you'll be like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.72,1:27:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会和你一样\N{\fs45}I won't do what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.26,1:27:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fs45}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.59,1:27:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以的  瓦莱丽\N{\fs45}Yes, you can, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.33,1:27:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的血管里流淌着我的血\N{\fs45}My blood already courses through your veins.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.43,1:27:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是礼物\N{\fs45}It's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.54,1:27:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我父亲给我的礼物\N{\fs45}It's a gift my father gave to me
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.18,1:27:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我也可以给你\N{\fs45}that now I can give to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.17,1:27:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比他强\N{\fs45}I'm stronger than he was,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.43,1:27:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甚至可以比我更强\N{\fs45}you'll be even stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.91,1:27:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想看吧\N{\fs45}Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.38,1:27:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将会所向披靡\N{\fs45}We will be invincible.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.75,1:27:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝一定存在  因为你就是那恶魔\N{\fs45}There must be a God, because you're the devil.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.42,1:27:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你是恶魔的女儿\N{\fs45}And you're the devil's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.99,1:28:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日出时  你就没那么可怕了\N{\fs45}You're not so terrifying when the sun is up.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.63,1:28:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fs45}How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.26,1:28:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs45}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.16,1:28:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西要给你\N{\fs45}I have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.77,1:29:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fs45}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.74,1:29:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我离开这里\N{\fs45}Get me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.99,1:29:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他咬了我\N{\fs45}He bit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.76,1:29:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮升起时\N{\fs45}When the moon rises...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.97,1:29:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会像他一样\N{\fs45}I'll be like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.90,1:29:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成一头野兽\N{\fs45}A beast.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.02,1:30:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所知的一切都被颠覆了\N{\fs45}Everything I knew was ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.85,1:30:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所见的一切都变了\N{\fs45}I saw it all differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.22,1:30:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是谎言  母亲的  父亲的\N{\fs45}All the lies. My mother's, my father's.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.73,1:30:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我仅剩的全部\N{\fs45}He was all I had left.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.80,1:30:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fs45}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.13,1:30:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我怀疑他\N{\fs45}Even when I doubted him...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.30,1:30:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即时我伤害他\N{\fs45}even when I wounded him...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.21,1:30:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得一直是真诚的\N{\fs45}Peter was true.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.76,1:30:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs45}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.02,1:32:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲的事不能让人知道\N{\fs45}No one can know about your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.15,1:32:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然他们会绞死你\N{\fs45}They'll hang you...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.09,1:32:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因你是狼人的女儿\N{\fs45}for being the daughter of the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.49,1:33:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fs45}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.19,1:33:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须得离开\N{\fs45}I have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.46,1:33:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我在一起不安全\N{\fs45}You won't be safe with me...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.26,1:33:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我学会怎样保护你之前\N{\fs45}until I learn how to protect you from....
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.67,1:34:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等你\N{\fs45}I'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.38,1:34:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说\N{\fs45}I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.74,1:34:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我记忆中最残酷的冬天\N{\fs45}It was the most brutal winter I could remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.16,1:34:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑角村又回到了往日的平静\N{\fs45}Daggerhorn fell back into its old rhythms.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.54,1:34:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人没有再出现\N{\fs45}The wolf didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.83,1:34:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但村民仍然生活在恐惧之中\N{\fs45}But the village still lived in fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.46,1:34:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他们唯一所知的生活\N{\fs45}It was the only life they knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.84,1:35:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利找到了勇气\N{\fs45}Henry found his courage.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.31,1:35:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着时间推移  母亲明白\N{\fs45}With time, my mother realized that
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.23,1:35:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲再也不会回到剑角村\N{\fs45}father would never return Daggerhorn.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.89,1:35:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护我们远离黑暗\N{\fs45}protecting us from darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.43,1:35:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他选择了光荣的人生之路\N{\fs45}He chose a life of honor
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.74,1:35:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再待在那里\N{\fs45}But I could no longer live there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.45,1:35:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有我的秘密\N{\fs45}with my secret

